quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Ta. Sin. Mim
  26,2,Tsena ke lits’enolo tsa Lengolo tse totobatsang
  26,3,"Kamohlomong u tla ituba moeeng ka ho utloa bohloko, hobane ba sa kholoe"
  26,4,"Hoja ebe ke Thato Ea Rona, Re ka be Re romela sesupo ho bona se tsoang marung, hore ba tle ba lule ba kebisitse melala ka boikokobetso"
  26,5,"Ka linako tsohle ha sehopotso se etla ho bona se secha se tsoang ho Ea Tletseng Lereko, ba ea furalla"
  26,6,Ba latola molaetsa; empa haufi ba tla tseba `nete ea seo ba ‘nileng ba se soma
  26,7,"Na ha ba es’o bone lefats’e, – hore ke mefuta e molemo ea lintho tseo Re li melisang teng"
  26,8,Ruri! Kahar’a sena ke sesupo; le hoja bongata ba bona bo sa lumele
  26,9,"Etsoe Ruri! Mong`a hau U Matla Oohle, Mohau oa Hae o’a Khaphatseha"
  26,10,"Mong`a hau U ile A bitsa Moshe: “Tsamaea o ee ho batho ba etsang liphoso"
  26,11,“Batho ba Faro. Na ba tla ts’aba Allah?”
  26,12,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ke t`saba hore ba tloha ba mphara ka leshano"
  26,13,"“Sefuba sa ka se tla petatsana. Puo ea ka e se hlake, kahoo nthome le Aarone"
  26,14,"“Ba bile ba na le qoso ea tlolo ea molao khahlano le ‘na, ka hona ke t`saba hore ba se tlohe ba mpolaea.”"
  26,15,"Allah A re: “Leletho, Tsoelang pele, bobeli ba lona ka lits’upiso tsa Rona. Ruri! Re tlabale lona, le hona ho le mamela"
  26,16,"“Joale, tsamaeang ‘moho le ee ho Faro, le re: “Re rometsoe ke ‘Maballi le Mong`a mafats’e ho uena"
  26,17,“Lokolla bana ba Israele ho tsamaea le rona.”
  26,18,"Faro a re: “Na ha re’a u holisa o le ngoana har’a rona? Oa lula lilemo tse ngata le rona bophelong ba hau"
  26,19,"“Eaba o etsa ketso eo u kileng oa e etsa, eo u e tsebang, oa ba e mong oa ba hlokang teboho!”"
  26,20,"Moshe a re: “Ke entse, nakong eo ke neng ke le ka har’a ba khelohileng"
  26,21,"“Ka lebaka la ho le t`saba ka baleha, Empa Mong`a ka U ile a nts’usumetsa ka taelo esita le hona ho nkhetha ke le e mong oa baromuoa ba Hae"
  26,22,"“Joale, sena ke ke tsela eo u mputsang ka eona, u nts’eolla ka hore: ke entse bana ba Israele makhoba.”"
  26,23,"Faro a re: “Joale, ke eng ‘Maballi le Mong`a mafats’e?”"
  26,24,"Moshe a re: “Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e le lintho tsohle tse teng lipakeng tsa ona, – haeba u batla ho rua tsebo.”"
  26,25,"Eaba faro o re ho ba neng ba mo pota-potile: “Na le’a utloa?”"
  26,26,"Moshe a re: “Mong`a lona le bo-ntat’a lona ho tloha ts’imolohong.”"
  26,27,"Faro a re: “Ruri! Moromuoa enoa ea romeletsoeng ho lona e feela e le lehlanya!”"
  26,28,"Moshe a re: “Mong`a bochabela le bophirima le tsohle tse lipakeng tsa tsona, ha feela ebale na le kutloisiso.”"
  26,29,"Faro a re: “Ha feela eba u ka ikhethela molimo e mong ntle ho ‘na, Ruri! Ke tla u koala chankaneng.”"
  26,30,"Moshe a re: “Le hoja ke u bonts’a se seng se hlakileng?”"
  26,31,"Faro a re: “Se bonts’e, haeba u e mong oa ba nang le ‘nete!”"
  26,32,"Eaba Moshe o akhela lere la hae fats’e, la fetoha noha"
  26,33,"A pholla lehlakore ka letsoho la hae, eaba le hlaha le le lesoeu ho babohi"
  26,34,"Faro a sebela Mahlahana a hae, a re: “Ruri! Enoa ke moloi oa sebele"
  26,35,"“Morero oa hae ke ho le phalalisa naheng ea lona ka mehlolo ena ea hae. Joale, ke eng seo le ka nkeletsang ka sona?”"
  26,36,"Ba re: “Ak’u ba boloke hanyane ka bobeli ba bona, joale e be u romella maqosa metseng"
  26,37,“Ba u tlisetse litsibi tsohle tsa boloi.”
  26,38,Baloi bohle ba bokelloa hammoho ka nako e boletsoeng mohla letsatsi le neng le khethiloe
  26,39,"Eaba ho thoe ho sechaba: “Na le se le khobokane hammoho?”"
  26,40,“Hore re tle re latele baloi haeba ba ka ikhapela tlholo?”
  26,41,"Eitse hoba baloi ba fihle ho faro, ba re ho eena: “Na ka ‘nete re tla fumana moputso haeba re fumana tlholo?”"
  26,42,"A re: “E ho joalo, e bile ka ‘nete le tla ba har’a ba atametseng haufi le ‘na.”"
  26,43,"Moshe a re ho bona: “Akhang lithebere tsa lona!”"
  26,44,"Eaba ba akha liketane le lithebere tsa bona, ba re: “Ruri! Ka matla a Faro, re tla ikhapela tlholo.”"
  26,45,"Moshe a akhela lere la hae fats’e, eaba le fetoha noha le koenya lintho tsohle tseo ba neng bali akhile ka ponts’o ea bohata"
  26,46,Eaba baloi ba oela fats’e ba ithapalatsa
  26,47,"Ba re: “Re kholoa ho Mong`a Mafats’e"
  26,48,“Mong`a Moshe le Aarone.”
  26,49,"Faro a re: “Le kholoa ho Eena joang ke’a s’o le nehe tumello. Ntle le khoao ke nkhekhe ea lona e le rutileng boloi! Empa ka ‘nete le tla tseba"
  26,50,"Ruri! Ke tla poma matsoho le maoto a lona mots’ekalle, e be ke’a le thakhisa kaofela ha lona.”"
  26,51,"Ba re: “Ha ho se ka re utloisang bohloko, hobane re tla boela ho Mong`a rona"
  26,52,"Takatso ea rona ke feela hore Mong`a rona o tla re ts’oarela libe tsa rona, hobane ke rona ba pele ba amohelang tumelo.”"
  26,53,"Eaba Re susumetsa Moshe: “Tsamaeang le makhabunyane A ka bosiu bohle, hobane le tla tla le setsoe morao.”"
  26,54,Kemoo Faro a ileng a romella maqosa metseng
  26,55,"A re: “Ruri! Ma-Israele ana ke lequloana le fokolang"
  26,56,“Ba khahlanong le rona
  26,57,“Re lebotho le hlometseng le malala-a-laotsoe.”
  26,58,"Ke kamoo Re ileng Ra ba lelekela thoko le lirapa, liliba tse ts’akhunyang"
  26,59,Matlotlong le maemong ohle a hlomphehang kateng
  26,60,"E joalo, Re ile Ra etsa hore bana ba Israele e be majalefa a lintho tseo"
  26,61,Ba ba beha meja esale ka matjeke
  26,62,"Ha bobeli bo bonana, ba neng ba ena le Moshe ba re: “Ruri! Re se re ts’oeroe.”"
  26,63,"Moshe a re: “Che, Mong`a ka o na le ‘na. Ke Eena ea tla ntataisa"
  26,64,"Eaba Re susumetsa Moshe: “Otla leoatle ka lere la hau.” Eaba leoatle le’a arohana, karolo e ngoe le e ngoe ea ipopa thajana"
  26,65,Eaba Re atametsa lichaba ka bobeli haufi le moo
  26,66,Re ile Ra pholosa Moshe le bohle ba neng ba ena le eena
  26,67,Eaba Re khamisa lebotho la Faro ka metsi
  26,68,Ruri
  26,69,"Empa Ruri! Mong`a hau o na le Matla Oohle, o Tletse Mohau"
  26,70,Ak’u ba phetele pale ea Abrahama
  26,71,"Mohla a neng a buoa le ntata’e le batho ba habo a re: “ke eng sena seo le se khumamelang?”"
  26,72,"Ba re: “Re khumamela lits’oants’o tse betliloeng, re ke ke ra khaohana le eona.”"
  26,73,"Abrahama a re: “Na li ea le utloa nakong eo le memetsang ho tsona, kapa hona ho le etsetsa botle kapa bobe"
  26,74,"Ba re: “Che, re fumana bo-ntat’a rona ba ntse ba li khumamela.”"
  26,75,"A re: “Na le’a bona eo le khumamelang"
  26,76,“Lona le bo-ntat’a lona pele ho lona
  26,77,“Kaofela ha tsona ke lira ho ‘na; empa e seng Mong`a mafats’e
  26,78,"«Ea ntlhotseng, Ke Eena ea ntataisang"
  26,79,“Ea mphepang le hona ho mpha metsi
  26,80,"«Ha ke kula, ke Eena ea mphekolang"
  26,81,"“Ea tla etsa hore ke shoe, A boele A ‘nehe bophelo hape"
  26,82,"“Eena Eo ke nang le khopolo ea hore, U tla nts’oarela libe tsa ka mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo"
  26,83,"“Mong`a ka! Ak’u nkekeletse bohlale, U be U nkopanye le bohle ba lokileng"
  26,84,“U mphe tlaleho e hlomphehileng melokong e tlang
  26,85,“U nketse e mong oa majalefa a Serapa sa Nyakallo
  26,86,“Ts’oarela ntate oa ka. Hobane le eena ke e mong oabakhelohileng
  26,87,“U tle u se ke oa ntlotlolla mohla letsatsi leo U tla tsosa batho ka lona
  26,88,“Letsatsi leo ka lona leruo le bara li ke keng tsa re thusa ka letho
  26,89,«Kantle le ea ikatamelitseng haufi le Allah ka pelo eohle
  26,90,“Serapa se tla atametsoa haufi le bohle ba nenang bobe
  26,91,“Lihele li tla hlahella ponts’eng ho bohle ba hlahlathellang bobeng
  26,92,"“Ho tla thoe ho bona: “E kae melingoana eo le neng le e khumamela"
  26,93,“Kantle ho Allah? Na eka le thusa le hona ho ithusa?”
  26,94,"“Joale, batla lahleloa ka sefutho ka har’a Lihele,-bona le ba hlahlathellang bobeng"
  26,95,“Le mabotho oohle a iblis hammoho
  26,96,“Ba tla phehisana khang kamoo
  26,97,"“Ruri! Ka Allah, ka ‘nete re bile phosong e totobetseng"
  26,98,“Nakong eo re neng re le lekanya le Mong`a Mafats’e
  26,99,“Le baeki ba rona ke ba neng ba khanathetse molato feela
  26,100,“Ha joale ha re na ‘muelli
  26,101,«Kapa ena motsoalle le ea hore utloela
  26,102,"“Hoja re ne re ka ba le monyetla oa ho khutlela morao, Ruri! Re ne re tla ba har’a ba kholoang!”"
  26,103,Ruri
  26,104,"Ruri! Mong’a hau, Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,105,Le batho ba habo Nooe ba kile ba nyelisa baromuoa ba Allah
  26,106,"Ngoana bo bona Nooe o ne a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le ts’abe"
  26,107,Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,108,"Kahoo, ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,109,Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ona holim’a sena; moputso oa ka o tsoa feela ho Mong`a mafats’e
  26,110,"Ka hona, ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele.”"
  26,111,"Ba re: “Re ka kholoa ho uena, empa batho ba eisehang ba u latetse morao?”"
  26,112,"A re: “Ke tseba joang ka tseo ba li etsang"
  26,113,"“Boikarabello ba bona bo ho Mong`a ka, hoja feela eba le utloisisa"
  26,114,“Ha ke’a tla ho tla phalalisa ba kholoang
  26,115,“Ke rometsoe ho hlokomelisa pepeneneng.”
  26,116,"Ba re: “Nooe, haeba u sa khaotse, u tla tlepetsoa ka majoe.”"
  26,117,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! Batho ba heso ba ea ntatola"
  26,118,"“Ak’u ahlole lipakeng tsa rona le bona ka kahlolo e senang leeme, U mpholose le ba kholoang bohle ba nang le ‘na.”"
  26,119,Eaba Re’a mo pholosa hammoho le bohle ba neng ba ena le eena ka Arekeng
  26,120,Kamor’a ho moo Ra khamisa bohle ba setseng ka metsi
  26,121,"Ruri ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona ha bo kholoe"
  26,122,"Ruri! Mong’a hau, Ke Eena Ea Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,123,Ba-Ad ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah
  26,124,"Ngoana bo bona Hud a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le ts’abe Allah"
  26,125,“Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,126,"“Kahoo, ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,127,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ona; moputso oa ka o ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,128,“Na le ka aha sefika holim’a leralla le leng le le leng ho ithabisa
  26,129,"“Le aha le matlo a matle a bolulo, khopolong ea ho phela teng kahosafeleng"
  26,130,"“Ha le sebelisa matla a lona, le ea sebelisa joalo ka batho ba nang le matla oohle"
  26,131,"“Ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,132,“Ts’abang Eena Ea le sitsitseng ka lintho tsohle tseo le li tsebang
  26,133,“U le setsitse ka makhomo le bara
  26,134,“Lirapa le liliba tse ts’akhunyang
  26,135,“Ke na le ts’abo ea Kahlolo ea mohla Letsatsi le Ts’abehang.”
  26,136,"Ba re: “Ho ea ts’oana ho rona hore na u oa re khalema kapa u ba sieo hara bakhalemi"
  26,137,"“Tsena ha se letho, haese tsona linthoana tsa mehleng ea khale"
  26,138,«Ha re ke ba ka amohelang mahloko kapa likahlolo!»
  26,139,"Ba ile ba mo latola; Ra ba ripitla. Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa boholo ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,140,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, Mohau Oa Hae o’a Khaphatseha"
  26,141,"Ba-Thamud, ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah"
  26,142,"Ngoana bo bona Salih a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le Ts’abe"
  26,143,“Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,144,"“Kahoo, ts’abang Allah, le ‘mamele"
  26,145,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang oona; moputso oa ka o ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,146,“Na le hopola hore le ts’ireletsong ka lintho tsohle tseo le nang le tsona hajoale
  26,147,“Lirapa le liliba tse ts’akhunyang
  26,148,“Masimo a poone le lifate tsa lipalema tse behileng haholo hooli ka ‘nang tsa robeha
  26,149,“Le hona ho honya mafika ho etsa matlo ka botsebi bo matla
  26,150,“Empa ts’abang Allah le ‘mamele
  26,151,“Le se latele taelo ea ea lehlasoa
  26,152,"“Ea jalang pherekano lefats’eng, ea sa rateng ho sokoloha.”"
  26,153,"Ba re: “uena u e mong oa ba louoeng"
  26,154,"“U motho joalo ka rona. Kahoo, hlahisa sesupo haeba u bua `nete.”"
  26,155,"Salih a re: “Bonang, kamele ke ena e ts’ehali. Le eona e na le tokelo ea ho noa Selibeng ka letsatsi le leng, le lona le na le tokelo e joalo ka letsatsi le leng, empa ka letsatsi le boletsoeng"
  26,156,«Le se e nt`se kotsi esere la tloha la oeloa ke Kahlolo ea Letsatsi le Ts’abehang.”
  26,157,"Empa ba ile bae khakhatha, eaba ba apareloa ke masoabi"
  26,158,"Ba oeloa ke kahlolo. Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,159,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,160,Batho ba habo Lota ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah
  26,161,"Ngoana’bo bona Lota a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le Ts’abe"
  26,162,‹Ke moromuoa ea t`sepahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,163,"“Kahoo, ts’abang Allah le ‘mamele"
  26,164,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ho lona; moputso oa ka o ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,165,“Har’a libopuoa tsohle lefats’eng le arorelana likobo le banna ba bang
  26,166,"“Le siee bao Mong`a lona a le hloletseng bona? Che, le batho ba tlotseng meeli eohle.”"
  26,167,"Ba re: “Oho Lota haeba u sa khaotse, ruri u tla lelekoa.”"
  26,168,"A re: “Ke hloile liketso tsa lona"
  26,169,“Mong`a ka! Ak’u mpholose le ba lelapa la ka ho tseo ba li etsang!”
  26,170,"Re ile ra mo pholosa ‘moho lebalelapa la hae,-bohle"
  26,171,“Ntle feela le mosali moholo ea neng a le har’a ba neng ba salatse morao
  26,172,Empa Ra ripitla bohle
  26,173,"Ra ba nesetsa majoe a lengetana: E ts’abehang pula ho ba neng ba khaleng’oe"
  26,174,"Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,175,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,176,Balekane ba Moru ba ile ba latola Baromuoa ba Allah
  26,177,"Shuaib a re ho bona: “Na le sa tla ke le Ts’abe"
  26,178,“Ke moromuoa ea ts’epahalang ea romiloeng ho lona
  26,179,“Kahoo ts’abang Allah le ‘mamele
  26,180,“Ha ho moputso oo ke le kopang ona; moputso oa ka o tsoa ho Mong`a mafats’e feela
  26,181,"«Fanang ka tekanyo e nepahetseng, le se ke la jalletsa"
  26,182,«Le be le bekhe ka nepo le ‹nete
  26,183,"“Le se ke la ja batho ling tsa bona, le ho etsa bokhopo ka ho fehla pherekano lefats’eng"
  26,184,“Le ts’abe Eena Ea le hlotseng le meloko pele ho lona.”
  26,185,"Ba re: “Uena u e mong oa ba louoeng"
  26,186,"“U motho joalo ka rona, re nahana hore u leshano"
  26,187,"“Ak’u etse hore lekumane la leholimo le re oele, haeba u buoa ‘nete.”"
  26,188,"A re: “Ke Mong`a ka Ea hlokolosi ka ho fetisisa malebana le tseo le li etsang.”"
  26,189,"Ba ile ba mo latola, eaba ba oeloa ke kotlo ea Letsatsi la mahlomola. Ruri! E bile Kotlo ea Letsatsi le Ts’abehang"
  26,190,"Ruri! ho sena ke sesupo, empa bongata ba bona bo sa kholoe"
  26,191,"Ruri! Mong’a hau U Matla Oohle, U Tletse Mohau"
  26,192,Ruri sena ke Ts’enolo e tsong ho Mong`a Mafats’e
  26,193,E theohile le moea oa ‘Nete le Tumelo
  26,194,"Pelong le kelellong ea hau, hore u tle u khaleme"
  26,195,Ka puo e mathemaloli ea Se-Arabia
  26,196,Kantle ho khoao e teng ka har’a mangolo a halalelang a batho ba khale-khale
  26,197,Ana ha se sesupo ho bona ha barutehi ba bana ba Israele ba e tseba
  26,198,Hoja e be Re ile Ra le senolela e mong oa sechaba ntle le sa Ma-Arab
  26,199,"A ba balla lona, ba ne ba ke ke ba kholoa ho lona"
  26,200,Ke kamoo re etsang hore le kene lipelong tsa Baetsa-libe
  26,201,Ba ke ke ba kholoa ho lona ho fihlela ba bona kahlolo e Mahlonoko
  26,202,Empa e tla ba fihlela ka ts’ohanyetso ba sa elelloe
  26,203,"Joale ba tla re: “Re tla fuoa nyehlisetso?”"
  26,204,Ana ba lakatsa ho potlakela kahlolong ea Rona
  26,205,Na u oa hlokomela? Hore haeba Re ka ba neha nyehlisetso ea lilemo tse ‘maloa
  26,206,Ha ho fihla kahlolo eo e saleng ba e ts’episoa
  26,207,Tsohle tseo e saleng ba ithabisa ka tsona li ke ke tsa ba thusa ka letho
  26,208,Ha ho motse oo Re kileng Ra o ripitla o sa kang oa romelloa bahlokomelisi
  26,209,"Molemong oa ho ba hopotsa, ha Re’a s’o ka Re eba bahanyapetsi"
  26,210,T`senolo ena ha e ea tlisoa ke bo-liabolosi lefats’eng
  26,211,"E bile ha e ea ba lokela, kapa ona matla a ho e hlahisa"
  26,212,Ruri! ba qheletsoe thoko le ho e utloa
  26,213,"Kahoo, u se bitse ho mang kapa mang ntle ho Allah, esere oa tloha oa ba e mong oa ba tla fumana kotlo"
  26,214,U khaleme ba leloko la hau ba haufi le uena
  26,215,U be pelo-tlhomohi ho Ba-kholoang ba u latelang
  26,216,"Empa haeba ba ke ke ba u mamela, e re: “Ruri! Ha ke na molato ho tseo le li etsang.”"
  26,217,"U behe ts’epo ea hau ho Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Tletseng Mohau"
  26,218,Eena Ea u bonang nakong eo u emeng u rapelang
  26,219,Ea bonang le boikokobetso ba hau har’a baithapalatsang thapelong
  26,220,Hobane Ke Eena Ea Utloang le ho tseba tsohle
  26,221,Ana nka le bolella ka bao bo-liabolosi ba theohelang holim’a bona
  26,222,"Ba theohela holim’a bohle ba leshano, ba khopo"
  26,223,"Ba ts’ollela litsebeng tsa bona lipuo tsa mafeela, boholo ba bona ba leshano"
  26,224,"Le Bareneketsi, – bohle ba fosahetseng ba ba sala morao"
  26,225,Ana ha u es’o bone kamoo ba khelohileng ba phaqola hoohle
  26,226,Le kamoo ba buoang ka seo ba sa se etseng
  26,227,"Kantle le ba kholoang, ba etsa liketso tse lokileng, le hona ho hopola Allah ka linako tsohle, le hona ho its›ireletsa kamor’a hoba ba tlatlaptjoe. Baetsalibe bona, haufinyane ba tla ruoa tsebo ka se seholo seo e tlang ho ba pheletso ea bona"